premise_source_doc_sentence: The franchise has also crossed over with DC Comics television shows which air on other networks ; Arrow crossed over with the short-lived NBC series Constantine in the former 's fourth season , while there have been multiple crossovers with the Supergirl TV series , primarily following its move from CBS to The CW .
The Flash is an American television series developed by Greg Berlanti , Andrew Kreisberg and Geoff Johns , airing on The CW .
